ZH: 我们的公司员工都加入了工会。
EN: All of our company employees have joined the union.

ZH: 工会代表提出了要求，希望得到更好的工作条件。
EN: The union representatives have proposed demands for better working conditions.

ZH: 工会成员明天将举行罢工。
EN: The union members will go on strike tomorrow.

ZH: 工会组织了一场抗议活动。
EN: The union organized a protest.

ZH: 工会为工人争取权益。
EN: The union fights for the rights of workers.

ZH: 工会集会吸引了许多人。
EN: The union rally attracted a large crowd.

ZH: 我在工会会议上被选为会长。
EN: I was elected president at the union meeting.

ZH: 工会为加薪方面进行了谈判。
EN: The union is negotiating for a pay raise.

ZH: 工会的目标是保护工人的利益。
EN: The goal of the union is to protect the interests of workers.

ZH: 工会提供了帮助，让我们更好地了解自己的权利。
EN: The union provided help to better understand our rights.

ZH: 工会代表与雇主就劳动合同进行了谈判。
EN: The union representative negotiated with the employer on the labor contract.

ZH: 工会工人举行了游行示威活动。
EN: Union workers held a protest march.

ZH: 工会为提高工资标准而努力。
EN: The union strives to increase wage standards.

ZH: 工会会员之间保持团结很重要。
EN: Solidarity among union members is important.

ZH: 工会提供法律援助服务。
EN: The union provides legal aid services.

ZH: 工会为雇员维权做出了巨大努力。
EN: The union has made great efforts to protect the rights of employees.

ZH: 工会在法律问题上发挥了重要作用。
EN: The union plays an important role in legal issues.

ZH: 工会已经投入了大量资源来支持工人的利益。
EN: The union has invested a lot of resources to support the interests of workers.

ZH: 工会代表在团队中拥有要求更高的地位。
EN: The union representatives hold a higher position in the team.
